300
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,600
I need a solution to today's crisis.

301
00:15:27,750 --> 00:15:28,600
Otherwise,

302
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:29,630
my family will get stuck.

303
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:33,840
I have to rely

304
