on Wei Yun's morals.

305
00:15:45,550 --> 00:15:46,390
Wei Yun?

306
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:48,750
Is it appropriate for you

307
00:15:48,750 --> 00:15:49,590
to come in so late?

308
00:15:49,750 --> 00:15:50,590
Chu Yu,

309
00:15:51,270 --> 00:15:52,720
