00:21:42,830 --> 00:21:44,440
Concerning some secrets,

398
00:21:44,830 --> 00:21:45,720
it will be perilous.

399
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:48,830
Though Ms. Chu is as excellent as men,

400
00:21:49,350 --> 00:21:51,400
men in our family
