424
00:23:48,240 --> 00:23:49,400
If I agree

425
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:50,510
to be honest with you,

426
00:23:53,680 --> 00:23:54,550
will you

427
00:23:54,550 --> 00:23:55,790
stay in my family

428
00:23:57,680 --> 00:23:59,030
