433
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:18,270
Until you accept it.

434
00:24:18,590 --> 00:24:19,430
You...

435
00:24:22,110 --> 00:24:23,670
Chu Yu. Chu Yu.

436
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:24,840
Chu Yu.

437
00:24:44,920 --> 00:24:45,760
It hurts.

438
00:24:49,590 --> 00:24:50,430
It hurts.

439
00:25:00,200 --> 00:25:01,040
Don't.

