00:25:05,440 --> 00:25:06,280
Don't.

442
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:29,080
Rest assured.

443
00:25:30,920 --> 00:25:32,070
I won't tell anyone.

444
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:41,240
I will take good care

445
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:42,200
of Her Ladyship.

446
00:25:43,000 --> 00:25:43,920
Your Lordship,

447
00:25:44,070 --> 00:25:45,440
