00:25:46,830 --> 00:25:47,670
Take care of her.

449
00:25:49,310 --> 00:25:50,310
If you need anything,

450
00:25:50,310 --> 00:25:51,160
ask Wei Qiu for it.

451
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:53,040
These days,

